parameters: Man, it's really dark up here...
I think this area used to be used for storage.
That would explain the lack of lights...
So we should probably just go back home then, right?
I can't stomach the thought of some creep hanging onto my panties...
\n[7] \n[4].\! I really think it might be time to give up on your underwear...
Do you have any idea how much they cost?!
Besides, as long as we stick together, we should be safe!
Just stay close to me, alright?
\n[1], this dresser has a lock on it.
Do you think there's something important in there?
Unlike the rest of this place, the lock isn't covered in dust.
So it must have been used recently, right?
That's what I'm thinking.\! Let's keep searching to see
if we can find a key!
Okay.\! Try out the key and see if it's the right one!
Don't keep me waiting!\! \BST[7]I want to see what's inside!
It's a pair of panties, alright...
Oh how I've missed you!\! \BST[6]And they're still in pristine condition too!
I was worried about the state that they'd be in but these
That's strange.\! If I found that pair of panties I would have-
I-\! \BST[6]I would have returned them to their rightful owner
Hey look.\! There's a note here too.
Dear Miss \n[4].\! I think these belong to you.
The other day, when I went to drop off Mom's desserts to you, after I walked out
I noticed these had caught on to my jacket.
I wasn't sure what to do about it since I thought you'd think I stole them on purpose!
My Dad is taking us on a vacation so I'm a little late
I promise I didn't touch them or do anything weird!
I even stored them in my super secret safe so no one would find them!
Please forgive me!\! I love showing you my new drawings so I
hope you don't stop talking to me.
So it was the apartment manager's son all along...
I always could tell he had a little crush on me.
It sounds like it was an honest accident too.
What a relief!\! \BST[4]I just hope the whole family's okay.
Well, they went on vacation because of their dad's health, right?
Maybe they're somewhere safe outside the city.
So now that the mystery's solved, we can get out of here right?!
Hang on.\! Can you see that on the wall \n[7] \n[4]?
Her hair has an awfully familiar coloring to it too...
It's shaded on the bottom part of it.
And this style of drawing...\! It can't be, could it?
Do you recognize it or something?
I think it came from down the hallway!
There's only one way to find out...
I know it's you.\! You can stop hiding now.
It's him.\! The apartment manager's son...
You mean you know this zombie?!
Yes.\! I don't think he wants to hurt us.
We won't harm you.\! But in return, you have to leave us alone too...
[Wait a second.\! Is it listening to her?!]
I came here to take back what was mine.\! We'll be leaving now.
We won't disturb your home anymore.\! \BST[3]But you have to stop snooping in
It's rude to follow a woman around.\! Okay?
Is he... letting us leave now?
That pour soul.\! We must have spooked it.
That thing nearly scared me half to death!
I'm never going to be able to sleep again after that...
Hey \n[1], what's that thing in the closet?
Darn.\! I was hoping it would be something useful.
Well, I'll hang onto it just in case.
I don't think that's really necessary dear...
I know it's scary but I don't think I can come back here a second time...
I think it's better that we just get this over with.
I almost feel like I can see something shining at the bottom of the tub.
No way am I putting my hand in that water though!
\n[1], look!\! There's something sparkling in the bottom of the tub!
Great find \n[7] \n[4]!\! I wonder if this will unlock that dresser in the other room?
There's only one way to find out.
I think this valve that we found can fit on this handle.
Now doesn't seem like the time for maintenance duty \n[1]...
I bet this is the key to your missing panties!
Go on.\! Give it a spin.
The water to the bath tub drained.
Maybe something can fit into it.
It's a crudely drawn picture of two people having sex...
The woman looks awfully similar to \n[7] \n[4]...
